Package org.ontal.imgutil.settings

Class ImageSize

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ontal.imgutil.settings.ImageSize
  • public final class ImageSize
extends Object
    Image dimensions configuration container class used by Settings. Along with normal fields and constructors contains a list of predefined constants of widths and heights for ratio dependent transformations.
    Since:
    May 2012
    Author:
    akaine
